'''"Project Black Harvest"''' was a secret [[The Adasca BioMechanical Corporation of Arkania|Adascorp]] project involving the research of [[Exogorth/Legends|exogorths]]. Director [[Artonian Dobonold]] and lead [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]] [[Gorman Vandrayk]] were known to work for it.

{{Science-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
As confirmed by [[John Jackson Miller]], the name "Black Harvest" is a reference to ''Blue Harvest'', the codename for [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="Faraway KotOR 20">{{Faraway|url=comics/swknights/swkotor20.html|text=''Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic #20''}}</ref>

Curiously, in the ''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]'' it is referred to as "Operation Dark Harvest".

